# LLM Chat via APIs

This project includes chat functionality with Large Language Models (LLMs) through their APIs.

- When working on chat or LLM-related code, consider API clients, request/response handling, and streaming where applicable
- Use official SDKs or well-maintained libraries for LLM providers (e.g., OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.)
- Keep API keys and secrets in environment variables or secure config, never in source code
